<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP7">
<l>kaiyi ṉārcuri caṅkaṉa lāḻiyar nīḷvaraipōl</l>
<l>meyya ṉārtuḷa pavirai yārkamaḻ nīṇmuṭiyem</l>
<l>maiya ṉāraṇi yaraṅkaṉā raravi ṉaṇaimicai mēya māyaṉār</l>
<l>ceyyavā yaiyō veṉṉaic cintai kavarntatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Aiyō! The red mouth—of the Wonderful Lord, who dwells upon the serpent- bed,</l>
<l>Him from the ornate Raṅgam, our revered Father with a lofty crown</l>
<l>emitting the scent of the abundantly fragrant tulsi,</l>
<l rend="indent">Him with a tall mountain-like body,</l>
<l>Him with a blazing discus [and] a spiralling conch in [His] hands—has stolen my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
